{"tid":406383,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"早來的生日快樂","createTime":"2017-09-19T15:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T15:18:10.000Z","uid":108524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8be83c632a1a471d310e36d15758df58dc76ec","tid":406383,"uid":108524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"dptksojsqqunotyjfsu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道今日唔係你生日，聽日先係，但係我都係忍唔住打咗俾你講生日快樂（希望你記得點解啦）⋯⋯分咗手呢幾年我覺得自己好垃圾乜都做唔到，以為冷處理就會忘記到你，但原來每年嘅罪疚感都會倍增。<br />\n其實你cut線我都預咗㗎喇，不過我都好想同你做返朋友（應該都好難好難哈哈），希望你讀書上莊住hall拍拖加油，始終你都係叻仔嚟，對你有十足十信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同fb上面嗰女仔都stay sweet啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b06f9e08ad4646d21725a60dad8c3090a2cb7c","tid":406383,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"你係阿希？"},{"pid":"29e8f14a03e29150f236e4916a5c734c6bc536a7","tid":406383,"uid":108524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7db12cccc1c98b5c7e08085e05618bdc4fe7ee6","tid":406383,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係阿希？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}